    TODO(compliance): NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypes pending sign-off from compliance counsel.
    Per docs/mobile-architecture.md §12, we must declare:
      - video recording (linked to user, not used for tracking)
      - performance data (Sentry — linked, not for tracking)
      - crash data (Sentry — linked, not for tracking)
      - email (account — linked, not for tracking)
